<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <title>Thank you for contacting Bailey's Kitchen</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      background-color: #f8f9fa;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .content {
      background-color: #ffffff;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      border: 1px solid #dee2e6;
    }
    .message-box {
      background-color: #f8f9fa;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 20px;
      color: #6c757d;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h2>Thank you for contacting Bailey's Kitchen!</h2>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
      <p>Dear {{name}},</p>
      
      <p>Thank you for reaching out to us. We have received your message and will get back to you as soon as possible.</p>
      
      <div class="message-box">
        <h3>Your Message Details:</h3>
        <p><strong>Subject:</strong> {{subject}}</p>
        <p><strong>Message:</strong></p>
        <p>{{message}}</p>
      </div>
      
      <p>If you have any additional questions or concerns, please don't hesitate to contact us again.</p>
      
      <p>Best regards,<br>Bailey's Kitchen Team</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content" style="margin-top: 20px;">
      <h3>Other Ways to Reach Us</h3>
      <div style="background-color: #f8f9fa; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px;">
        <p><strong>Email:</strong> support@baileyskitchen.com</p>
        <p><strong>Phone:</strong> +91 8939660833</p>
        <p><strong>Address:</strong><br>Bangalore, India<br>560035</p>
        <p><strong>Business Hours:</strong><br>
          Monday - Friday: 9:00 AM - 6:00 PM PST<br>
          Saturday: 10:00 AM - 4:00 PM PST<br>
          Sunday: Closed</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
      <p>This is an automated response. Please do not reply to this email.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html> 